des: Fancy Radio is a broadcasting radio station located in London UK, It is distinguished by its program’s combination of news, live talk, current affairs, music, and sports. It is also broadcast via the Internet in the rest of the country and worldwide. Fancy Radio is one of the most listened-to radio stations in London.
